BEFORE INSTALLING
====== ==========

   REQUIREMENTS
   ------------

   The NS2Html scripts were written in Perl. This way, some modules was
necessary to become easy the developer's life. The only module used on the
scripts is the following:

   - Getopt::Std

INSTALLING THE NS2HTML
========== === =======

   INSTALATION PROCEDURES
   ----------- ----------

   Step 1 - The steps bellow  must be followed. ;)
   Step 2 - Unpacking the source file

   # gunzip ns2html-0.4.1.tar.gz
   # tar -xvf ns2html-0.4.1.tar

   Step 3 - Done. Too hard, huh?!!!

SECURITY CONSIDERATIONS
======== ==============

   In this version, Mysql is not even more required. So, non-admin users
can use NS2HTML on their Netscreen config files.

   In order to get some security (I hope), we recommend that you store 
your Netscreen's backups on a directory with a good level of security.
